Sierra Leone administrative area level 3 - chiefdom

Source: R/data.R
chiefdom.Rd

Sierra Leone administrative area level 3 - chiefdom

chiefdom

Format

A SpatialPolygonsDataFrame with 167 features:

OBJECTID

Object Identifier

admin3Name

Name of administrative area level 3

admin3Pcod

Postal code of administrative area level 3

admin3RefN

Reference of administrative area level 3

admin3AltN

Alternative name of administrative area level 3

admin3Al_1

Alternative name of administrative area level 3

admin2Name

Name of administrative area level 2

admin2Pcod

Postal code of administrative area level 2

admin2RefN

Reference of administrative area level 2

admin2AltN

Alternative name of administrative area level 2

admin2Al_1

Alternative name of administrative area level 2

admin1Name

Name of administrative area level 1

admin1Pcod

Postal code of administrative area level 1

admin1RefN

Reference of administrative area level 1

admin1AltN

Alternative name of administrative area level 1

admin1Al_1

Alternative name of administrative area level 1

admin0Name

Name of administrative area level 0

admin0Pcod

Postal code of administrative area level 0

date

Date

validOn

Valid on

validTo

Valid to

Shape_Leng

Shape length

Shape_Area

Shape area

Source

https://data.humdata.org/dataset/sierra-leone-all-ad-min-level-boundaries

chiefdom
